OL,3,CSoup Kitchen returns to Jersey for its
OL,4,C26th year
OL,6,FJersey's annual event which aims to
OL,7,Fraise money for homelessness has
OL,8,Freturned for its 26th year.
OL,10,F'Soup Kitchen' raises funds for The
OL,11,FShelter Trust and increases awareness
OL,12,Fof homelessness on the island by
OL,13,Fencouraging the public to buy one of
OL,14,F40 soups cooked for the occasion.
OL,16,FIslanders will be served a variety of
OL,17,Fdonated soups from 10:30am until 2pm
OL,18,Ftoday (Tuesday 10 December) in the
OL,19,FRoyal Square.
