OL,3,CSoup Kitchen returns to Jersey for its
OL,4,C26th year
OL,6,FRichard Robbins, Treasurer of The
OL,7,FShelter Trust, explains how the day
OL,8,Ftakes a different approach to help
OL,9,Fthose in need:
OL,11,F"The whole idea is that it is a
OL,12,Freverse Soup Kitchen, in that we
OL,13,Faren't serving soup for the homeless,
OL,14,Fwe are serving soup to the public
OL,15,Fdonated by all the local hotels and
OL,16,Frestaurants and all the money we raise
OL,17,Fhelps the homeless.
