OL,3,CSoup Kitchen returns to Jersey for its
OL,4,C26th year
OL,6,F"This is very important. Last year we
OL,7,Fraised over #27,000. It is important
OL,8,Fthat we make people aware of
OL,9,Fhomelessness in Jersey. The Trust
OL,10,Flooks after more than 100 people a
OL,11,Fnight.
OL,13,F"We are going to serve around 3000
OL,14,Fpeople so that raises their awareness
OL,15,Fof it."
OL,17,FHe continues: "It's absolutely vital
OL,18,Fthat people become aware that
OL,19,Fparticularly around Christmas there is
OL,20,Fhomeless around Jersey and that people
OL,21,Fdo something about it."
